{"id":415,"date":"2024-08-02T17:54:05","date_gmt":"2024-08-02T17:54:05","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=415"},"modified":"2024-08-02T17:54:05","modified_gmt":"2024-08-02T17:54:05","slug":"tm007-hail","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm007-hail\/","title":{"rendered":"TM007 Hail"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">TM007 Hail<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Gift from the clown in the Icy Hole cave South of Bellin Town after pushing him off of the slippery ice area.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Description<\/th>\n<td>A hailstorm lasting five turns damages all Pok\u00e9mon except the Ice-type.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>PP<\/th>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Ice<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Bellin Town<\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm08-rock-climb\/\">Rock Climb<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Starting from the Bellin Town Pok\u00e9mon Center, go South.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-bellin-town-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Bellin Town Pok\u00e9mon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Bellin Town Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll find a marker in the Southwest corner of the town indicating that you can use Rock Climb to enter the Icy Hole.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/02-pokemon-unbound-using-rock-climb-to-enter-the-icy-hole.jpg\" alt=\"Using Rock Climb to enter the Icy Hole. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using Rock Climb to enter the Icy Hole.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After entering the hole, follow the linear path forward.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/03-pokemon-unbound-going-north-after-entering-the-hole.jpg\" alt=\"Going North after entering the hole. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going North after entering the hole.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You want to land North of the clown in the slippery ice area.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/04-pokemon-unbound-interacting-with-the-clown-from-his-north.jpg\" alt=\"Interacting with the clown from his North. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Interacting with the clown from his North.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Speaking with the clown will give you the prompt to either push him or leave him there. Click the prompt to push him.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/05-pokemon-unbound-pushing-the-clown-downward.jpg\" alt=\"Pushing the Clown downward. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Pushing the Clown downward.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go to the clown\u2019s West and push him again to rescue him from the ice.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/06-pokemon-unbound-pushing-the-clown-to-rescue-him-from-the-ice.jpg\" alt=\"Pushing the Clown to rescue him from the ice. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Pushing the Clown to rescue him from the ice.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Now, all that\u2019s left is to speak with him to get the TM for Hail.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/07-pokemon-unbound-speaking-with-the-clown-to-get-the-tm-for-hail.jpg\" alt=\"Speaking with the clown to get the TM for Hail. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Speaking with the clown to get the TM for Hail.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">TMs &#038; HMs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":416,"parent":139,"menu_order":0,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[8],"class_list":["post-415","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tms-hms"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/415","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/139"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/416"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=415"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=415"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}